Package station

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LeastOccupiedComparator
    This class allows the system to sort stations in accordance with the occupation rate, from the least occupied to the most.
    MostUsedComparator
    This class allows the system to sort stations in accordance with the sum of rents + returns.
    ParkingSlot
    Class representing station parking slot.
    PlusStation
    Class representing plus station.
    SlotCreator
    Factory class used exclusively to create slots for each station according to parameters that may change, namely minimal percentage of occupied slots and minimal percentage of electric bikes.
    Station
    Class representing station.
    StationBalance
    This class implements all functions necessary to keep relevant information or statistics of a station.
    Terminal
    This class serves as the interface for the user when he is renting bikes.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SlotStatus
    Enum type containing possible status for parking slot.
